data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2-1/2 bath home with 2022 square feet in Northranch with a pool and spa on a cul-de-sac lot! The kitchen has been renovated with quartz counters, new cabinets, breakfast bar and pantry. The owner's suite bath has been completely renovated with new tile shower and dual sinks, new toilets throughout and walk-in closet. You will love the new secondary bath with stylish wall paper, new lighting, mirror and cabinet. The large yard is low-care with pavers, planters, and turf. New HVAC system in 2019 and no poly pipes! Don't miss this one.
